								p Charges were filed on February 23, 2017. A superseding incitement was filed on June 22, 2017.
								p He had pleaded not guilty.
								p A trial is tentatively scheduled for January.
					.profile
						.profile__content
							.image.image--officer
								img(src=datalink + "images/officer-snell.jpg")
								p Officer
							.text
								h3 Officer Eric Snell
								p Charged with conspiracy to distribute and possession with intent to distribute heroin and cocaine on November 9, 2017
								p Snell has been a Philadelphia officer for three years. He previously served as a Baltimore police officer, from July 2005 to March 2008.
								p He has not entered a plea.
								p His next court date hasn’t been scheduled.
