								h3 Sgt. Thomas Allers
								p Charged with racketeering conspiracy, racketeering, robbery on August 24, 2017
								p Pleaded guilty on Dec. 6 to racketeering conspiracy
								p Allers faces a maximum sentence of 20 years in prison.
								p He will be sentenced on Feb. 23.
				.orgChart__row
