							.text
								h3 Det. Momodu Bondeva Kenton Gondo
								p Charged with racketeering conspiracy and racketeering aiding and abetting on February 23, 2017
								p Charged with conspiracy to distribute and possession with intent to distribute heroin; and possession with intent to distribute and distribution of heroin and cocaine on February 17, 2016
								p He pleaded guilty to one count of racketeering conspiracy and one count of conspiracy to distribute and possess with intent to distribute 100 grams or more of a mixture or substance containing heroin.
								p Gondo faces as much as 40 years in prison--the longest maximum penalty of the indicted officers.
								p His sentencing hasn’t been scheduled.
